We want to build a calculator
features
-add
-substract
-multiply
- divide
flow
-you will ask the user to choose what they want to do 
- ask them for the first number
- ask them for the second number
- perform the operation
- show them the result ( the addition of x and y is w)
- ask them if they want to do another thing
    - if the answer is yes, repeat all those steps
    - if the answer is no, stop the program and tell them thank you